rgest dollar-pegged cryptocurrencies, as a government clampdown on the sect=
or widens.=C2=A0
The New York Department of Financial Services ordered Paxos Trust Co., whic=
h issues and lists Binance=E2=80=99s dollar-pegged cryptocurrency, to stop =
