awyers who probably used to work at your office, with suggestions for how y=
ou should best regulate crypto. They seemed nice and earnest, and you took =
their suggestions seriously.</li>=09<li style=3D"margin-bottom: 5px;">In 20=
23, you probably think =E2=80=9Cah, yes, this entity is doing a fraud, and =
plans to steal the money or crypto.=E2=80=9D</li>
</ul>
